{
  "stem": "17299.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they took some of-- said some more houses had been opened up-- and took some people out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were later on probably 20 in two rooms.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we-- we found some food on the table, which was frozen, and we found a lot of things, and so much clothing and everything.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we couldn't figure out what happened here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How did your family settle in, Alfred, into that room?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we decided-- there were some mattresses on the floor-- that the older people will sleep on the mattresses tonight and we the younger people will sleep on the floor, because we all had a blanket.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we made some fire in the oven because there was enough wood.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had some sandwiches, and there was water.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were a number of houses, but we were limited to one street-- to only on the right-hand side of the street from one corner to the other.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On both ends of the street were Latvian guards with rifles.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So if you would go further, they would shoot you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The name of the street was Virsaisu iela. 'Iela' is street.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the street was later on named, for the transport of Dusseldorf, Dusseldorfer Strasse.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the house was number four where I was living in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were fences all around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we saw the fences 24 hours later when we were marched-- we were marched out to the harbor to work.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On the other side from the fence were Jews with two stars, one on the left-hand side of the breast and one in the middle of the back, without any inscription in it-- just yellow stars.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We only saw male.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No female at all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We could not make any contact.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
